## Day 3 - Scrum Meeting summary
The Scrum Master for this meeting was Joshua Bradley

### Members Present:
Josh, James S, James R, Luke, Harry, Jesse, Alan

### Members Not Present:


### Summary of Conversation:
We went through what we achieved the previous day which included: setting up an ethics form, setting up local databases with WAMP for testing purposes, pair programming, 
and design changes.
Then we discussed our plans for the day which involved finalising the ethics form, continuing with general PHP/Javascript development.
Luke brought up an issue about different relationship types within our ER diagram (and thus the database). Harry took the lead in solving this quickly.
We quickly reviewed agile methods to ensure we stayed on track.

