The Scrum Master for this meeting was Joshua Bradley

### Members Present:
Josh, James S, James R, Luke, Harry, Jesse, Alan

### Members Not Present:


### Summary of Conversation:
We went through what we achieved the previous day which included: finalising the ethics form and working on the questionnaire making page.
Then we discussed our plans for the day which involved: trying to finish the questionnaire making page, 
