## Day 5 - Scrum Meeting summary
The Scrum Master for this meeting was Joshua Bradley

### Members Present:
Josh, James S, James R, Luke, Harry, Jesse, Alan

### Members Not Present:


### Summary of Conversation:
We started by going through what everyone had done the previous day, which was mainly working on questionnaire-making functionality.
Then we went through what we planned to do for the day (with an emphasis on finishing features for the sprint 1 review)
After that, we predicted any future issues. James R brought up a web design issue and James S volunteered to pair program and help.
Finally, we planned a meeting for 12:00 to practise our sprint 1 review.

